\forall r \exists n (r^n=r)
R
\,D\,
\,d\in D\,
\,d^n=d\,\,,\,\,1<n\in\Bbb N\,
d^n=d=\Longrightarrow d(d^{n-1}-1)=0\Longleftrightarrow d=0\,\,\,or\,\,\,d^{n-1}=1
-------o----------o---------o---
\,I\leq R\,
\, r\in R\setminus I\,
\exists\,n\in\Bbb N\,\,s.t.\,\,r^n=r\Longrightarrow \left(r+I\right)^n=r^n+I=r+I\in R/I
\,D:=R/I\,\,\,,\,\,d=r+I\,
\,R/I\,
